<ElliciumText Anchor="dropdown#keyboard-navigation" TextStyle="TextStyle.H5" TagName="TagName.H2" class="rz-pt-12">
    Keyboard Navigation
</ElliciumText>
<ElliciumText TextStyle="TextStyle.Body1" class="rz-mb-8">
    The following keys or key combinations provide a way for users to navigate and interact with Ellicium Blazor DropDown component.
</ElliciumText>

<div class="rz-data-grid rz-datatable rz-datatable-scrollable" style="width: 100%;">
    <div class="rz-data-grid-data">
        <table class="rz-grid-table">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th style="padding: var(--rz-grid-cell-padding)">Press this key</th>
                    <th style="padding: var(--rz-grid-cell-padding)">To do this</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td><span class="rz-cell-data"><ElliciumBadge Text="Tab" /></span></td>
                    <td><span class="rz-cell-data">Navigate to a DropDown.</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><span class="rz-cell-data"><ElliciumBadge Text="Alt" /> + <ElliciumBadge Text="Down arrow" /></span></td>
                    <td><span class="rz-cell-data">Open DropDown popup.</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><span class="rz-cell-data"><ElliciumBadge Text="Down Arrow" /> on closed popup</span></td>
                    <td><span class="rz-cell-data">Select next DropDown item.</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><span class="rz-cell-data"><ElliciumBadge Text="Up Arrow" /> on closed popup</span></td>
                    <td><span class="rz-cell-data">Select previous DropDown item.</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><span class="rz-cell-data"><ElliciumBadge Text="Down Arrow" /> in an opened popup</span></td>
                    <td><span class="rz-cell-data">Focus next DropDown item.</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><span class="rz-cell-data"><ElliciumBadge Text="Up Arrow" /> in an opened popup</span></td>
                    <td><span class="rz-cell-data">Focus previous DropDown item.</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><span class="rz-cell-data"><ElliciumBadge Text="Enter" /> in an opened popup</span></td>
                    <td><span class="rz-cell-data">Select the focused DropDown item and close the popup.</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><span class="rz-cell-data"><ElliciumBadge Text="Esc" /> or <ElliciumBadge Text="Alt" /> + <ElliciumBadge Text="Down arrow" /> in an opened popup</span></td>
                    <td><span class="rz-cell-data">Close the DropDown popup.</span></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><span class="rz-cell-data"><ElliciumBadge Text="Alphanumeric" /></span></td>
                    <td><span class="rz-cell-data">Focus next DropDown item starting with typed key.</span></td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
</div>
